dct_description_sm: Road map of Ocean County, New Jersey developed from a February 1934 map of State Dept. of Cons. and Devel. by Clinton Shinn, Jr. with numerous revisions up to 1951. Legend indicates road types for existing roads including unimproved, gravel, tar and concrete as well as roads under construction.
Some discoloration at noticeable wear at folds.
